<br>
For instance, a while back Legacy of Steel was selling rights to loot NToV loot. Most of their guild and Twinks had all they could use  so they offered to sell it. Then CoH you in for you to loot. They may have finally moved out of NToV  but still cleared  as much as they could right up until moving into VT.<br>
<br>
Maybe it is  just the Nameless, that has this problem but there is a guild on about 24/7 which can wipe  out NToV, AoW, and Tunare.  Either European-Remedy , or TW-Kylin Eyes or US-LoS, Euphoria, Crimson Tempest. <br>
<br>
Even when they do not need the items   or they use ony to twink characters or sell dropables.<br>
<br>
I know i may seem to be  whining a bit,  to many of you that have played awhile. But hey  this is just Norath as I  have seen it.   I mostly posting to  blow off frustration. After all I am  so addicted I play 7 days a week and love raiding. If i had started from the early days, or had  contacts in top guilds when i began playing.  i would probably be in the  High end game now.  <p><center>
